      <abstract>
        <p>Andre Agassi, defending Olympic gold medalist in men's singles, announces that he is withdrawing from Sydney Olympics; makes it clear that he is doing so because both his sister, Tammee, and his mother, Elizabeth, have breast cancer (S)</p>
